    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">ДАЛОЛАТНОМА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-style: italic;\">(</span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Маҳсулотларнинг номи</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">ни топшириш ва қабул қилиш тўғрисида</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-style: italic;\">)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#2}Далолатнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#3}Далолатнома тузилган жой</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"\">{#12}Маҳсулотларни топшираётган ташкилот номи ва ташкилий ва ҳуқуқий шакли</span> ҳамда <span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"\">{#13}Маҳсулотларни қабул қилиб олаётган ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span> ўртасида <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"\">{#14}Ишларни бажариш учун асос бўлган шартнома санаси</span> куни <span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"\">{#15}Ишларни бажариш учун асос бўлган шартнома рақами</span>-сонли шартнома тузилган. Шартномага кўра <span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"\">{#12}Маҳсулотларни топшираётган ташкилот номи ва ташкилий ва ҳуқуқий шакли</span> <span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"\">{#11}Маҳсулотларнинг номи</span> каби ишларни бажариб бериши белгиланган.</p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\">Юқоридаги шартномадан келиб чиққан ҳолда <span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"\">{#12}Маҳсулотларни топшираётган ташкилот номи ва ташкилий ва ҳуқуқий шакли</span> томонидан <span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"\">{#17}Маҳсулотларнинг тавсифи</span> <span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"\">{#11}Маҳсулотларнинг номи</span> топширилди. </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\">Қабул қилувчи ушбу маҳсулотларни қабул қилиб олди. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Топширувчи: </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"\">{#5}Маҳсулотларни топшираётган шахснинг лавозими</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"\">{#6}Маҳсулотларни топшираётган шахснинг Ф.И.Ш</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Қабул қилувчи:</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"\">{#8}Маҳсулотларни қабул қилаётган ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"\">{#9}Маҳсулотларни қабул қилаётган масъул шахснинг Ф.И.Ш.си</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
